       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI68101         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV6810.
       COPY COCV6811.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY TGCL1000.
       COPY TGCL2000.
       COPY TGCK0002.
      *
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 WS-PROGNAME  PIC X(08) VALUE 'COI68101'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CEMPRESA      PIC X(05) VALUE 'CO502'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CFUNCIONARIO  PIC X(05) VALUE 'CO507'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CANO          PIC X(05) VALUE 'AR111'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CMES          PIC X(05) VALUE 'AR112'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CIDPROJ       PIC X(05) VALUE 'CO151'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CIDDESP       PIC X(05) VALUE 'CO021'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CMOED         PIC X(05) VALUE 'AR041'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-CTABELA                   PIC X(05) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-NUMERICO                  PIC 9(03).
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-NUMERICO.
              10 WS-CODIGO                 PIC X(03).
           05 WS-CCOD                      PIC X(40) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-C2COD                     PIC X(40) VALUE SPACES.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI68101         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
