              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV6811-XDESCCEMPRESA     EQUAL SPACES
           AND COCV6811-CEMPRESA      NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CEMPRESA
                TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE COCV6811-CEMPRESA
                TO WS-CCOD
              MOVE SPACES
                TO WS-C2COD
              PERFORM 2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA
                 THRU 2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA-EXIT
              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE TGCL1000-GDESC
                   TO COCV6811-XDESCCEMPRESA
